Package: clinicalTrialSimulator
Type: Package
Title: Clinical Trial Data Simulation Package
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jorge", "AlcÃ¡ntara", email = "Jorge.alcantara.espinosa@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to simulate clinical trial data including patient demographics,
    treatment allocation, dropouts (including those related to adverse events), time-to-event outcomes,
    longitudinal repeated measures, and exporting a subject-level analysis dataset (ADSL).
    The package supports multi-level trial structures (e.g., countries and sites) and innovative features
    like dropout due to simulated adverse events.
